<template><h1 id="tabs-标签页" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#tabs-标签页" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Tabs 标签页</h1>
<h2 id="需求与-api-设计" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#需求与-api-设计" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 需求与 API 设计</h2>
<ul>
<li>点击时展现对应内容</li>
<li><code>g-tabs</code>设置<code>selected</code>的 props 初始选中内容 , 每个元素要加上对应的 <code>name</code></li>
<li>下面有横线平滑移动</li>
<li>标签页的方向(横向 , 纵向)</li>
<li><code>g-tabs-head</code>里需要一些额外操作的话, 可以用具名插槽搞定</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-html ext-html line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-html"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>template</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs</span> <span class="token attr-name">selected.sync</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>selectedTab<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token comment">&lt;!-- 等于 --></span>
    <span class="token comment">&lt;!-- &lt;g-tabs selected.sync="sports" @update:selected="selectedTab = $event">   --></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-item</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>women<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>美女<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-item</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-item</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>finance<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>财经<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-item</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-item</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>sports<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>运动<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-item</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>template</span> <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">v-slot:</span>actions</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>button</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>额外的操作<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>template</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-pane</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>women<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>美女相关<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-pane</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-pane</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>finance<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>财经相关<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-pane</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>g-tabs-pane</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>sports<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>运动相关<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-pane</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs-body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>g-tabs</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>template</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
